text: Jens Sørensen (4 April 1941 - 21 November 2020) was a Danish cyclist. He competed in the team pursuit at the 1960 Summer Olympics. He was born in Copenhagen. Sørensen died on 21 November 2020 at the age of 79. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Danish cyclists Category:Olympians for Denmark Category:Sportspeople from Copenhagen
